# textdomain: mcl_compass
Compass=指南针
Points to the world origin=指向世界原点
Compasses are tools which point to the world origin (X@=0, Z@=0) or the spawn point in the Overworld.=指南针是指向世界原点（X@=0，Z@=0）或主世界的出生点的工具。
A Compass always points to the world spawn point when the player is in the overworld.  In other dimensions, it spins randomly.=当玩家在主世界时，指南针总是指向世界重生点。 在其他维度，它随机旋转。
Lodestone Compass=磁石指南针
Points to a lodestone=指向磁石
Lodestone compasses resemble regular compasses, but they point to a specific lodestone.=磁石指南针类似于常规指南针，但它们指向特定的磁石。
A Lodestone compass can be made from an ordinary compass by using it on a lodestone.  After becoming a lodestone compass, it always points to its linked lodestone, provided that they are in the same dimension.  If not in the same dimension, the lodestone compass spins randomly, similarly to a regular compass when outside the overworld.  A lodestone compass can be relinked with another lodestone.=磁石指南针可以通过在磁石上使用普通指南针制成。 成为磁石罗盘后，它总是指向与其相连的磁石，前提是它们处于同一维度。 如果不在同一个维度，磁石罗盘会随机旋转，类似于在主世界之外的普通罗盘。 磁石指南针可以与另一个磁石重新链接。
